15:31:02:LNet: Service thread pid 30437 completed after 110.06s. This indicates the system was overloaded (too many service threads, or there were not enough hardware resources).
15:31:02:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  recovery-small test_10a: @@@@@@ FAIL: failed to chmod \/mnt\/lustre: 1 
